wiki.content:
Bridgit shot to fame as Teddy in the Disney TV series 'Good Luck Charlie' (where she also sings the show's theme tune). 'Ready Or Not' became a chart success in March 2013. “I wanted to write something that was empowering for girls”, she says of the track. “I consider myself to have been that girl sitting on the curb waiting for the world to notice”.
